{
  "stem": "23278.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if I wake up at night, night is finished.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Germany?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, once, to see my friend Wolf Schieck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My first sabbatical, I decided I'm going to see him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- he was a professor and of course, he was not in good state with his superiors, who were all Nazis, anyway.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when he wanted to get his job back, he needed some testimony and I explained to my first husband what had happened.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're going to do something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he figured out something-- all in capital letter, with big stamps, American stuff, saying that Wolf Schieck had been an exemplary man, and that he had helped people, and that he should be reinstated.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was reinstated like that-- because of my husband who was a generous, kind man and understood me and wanted to make me happy.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So Wolf got his job back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't have much, because he came from Prussia, and Prussia was invaded by the Russian.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His wife and his daughter just made it in time to Gottingen, and that's where I went to see them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I can tell you then, when I was in the train going from Paris to Frankfurt, and then to Hanover near Gottingen, and I was in that train at night and I could hear the-- you know the track going boom-boom boom-boom.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was thinking of the people in the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could almost not bear it and that's why I never went back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went to see him, we spoke of all that, and we went to a restaurant where everything was written in Gothic letter.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember it had-- [SPEAKING GERMAN], if you know German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It means veal-- breast of veal.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
